      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape, super clean inside and out, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and help you get behind the wheel!",
