    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S features the legendary 3.6L flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row retrofit, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a low-temp thermostat and high-flow water pump. Suspension remains taut with recently refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior shows honest patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and leak-down numbers\u2014remain within factory spec. A true driver\u2019s car with the wide-body aesthetic and enhanced grip of the viscous-coupled all-wheel-drive system.",
