      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of performance and luxury. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road peppering consistent with careful use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, complemented by a fully functional infotainment system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, it is sound; it has been serviced regularly at authorized centers, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine. The tires have plenty of tread remaining on the clean alloy wheels. It\u2019s a reliable, eye-catching drive that has been garage-kept and smoke-free. Documentation of recent oil changes and brake inspections is available. Ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
