      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This model has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring a seamless blend of performance and comfort for its next owner. With its clean profile and well-preserved interior, it represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver who values both integrity and value. Rigorously inspected and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
