    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car that's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, and it looks great inside and out. It\u2019s the perfect reliable ride for anyone looking for quality without that brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
