      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "An exceptional driver\u2019s example of the E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced VANOS system, ensuring mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering sharp turn-in and balanced lateral grip. Recent cooling system overhaul and fluid analysis confirm this chassis is ready for spirited engagement.",
